<text><body>
<pb ed="D" id="D08.8780.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><juan fun="open" n="1"><jhead>小鈔一卷</jhead></juan>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><div1><p id="pD08p0001a0201">&CB21868;欲發起先知教至歸三藏&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/>多羅&CB18911;<note place="inline">此云經藏</note>二毗柰耶&CB18911;<note place="inline">此云律&CB18911;&unrec;…&unrec;</note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><p id="pD08p0001a0401">今此四分戒本三&CB18911;之中&unrec;毗尼&CB18911;&unrec;…&unrec;。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a05"/><list><item id="itemD08p0001a0501">一名為戒<note place="inline">若就教釋防非為戒若就&unrec;…&unrec;&CB08891;為戒又單釋防非止&CB08891;名&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0001a06"/>律又釋詮量輕重&CB00804;&CB07589;是非名之為律若就行釋調伏&CB12919;鎔以之為律</note></item><item id="itemD08p0001a0628">三&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0001a07"/><note place="inline">若就教釋此是解縛之法依而出家者&unrec;…&unrec;故云彼〃解脫也若就行釋&unrec;縳之心念〃之中&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0001a08"/>&unrec;羈縳念〃離塵染名木叉</note></item><item id="itemD08p0001a0812">四名毗&CB00112;<note place="inline">&unrec;是&unrec;…&unrec;
<pb ed="D" id="D08.8780.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/>&CB07589;除生死苦盡&CB07099;為淡泊故名為滅又釋滅除生死盡諸苦&CB10318;故云毗尼</note></item></list><p id="pD08p0002a0129" place="inline">此毗&CB00112;&CB18911;世尊&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>傳臨涅槃時以此律&CB18911;付&CB21890;優波離滅度&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/>訶迦葉涅槃付&CB21890;阿難滅度付&CB21890;高&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/>修涅槃付&CB21890;優波&CB00545;多<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">己</rdg></app>上五大師佛法皆同一味
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/>後&CB00545;多有五&CB05663;子各&CB15137;生異見遂分為五。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/><list><item id="itemD08p0002a0601">一名&CB16765;婆多即十誦律主是也</item><item id="itemD08p0002a0613">二名曇無得即四分律主是</item>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/><item id="itemD08p0002a0701">三名&CB12752;沙塞即五分律主是也</item><item id="itemD08p0002a0713">四名婆&CB00308;富那即僧祇律
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/>主是也</item><item id="itemD08p0002a0804">五名迦葉毗律本未來漢地也</item></list><p id="pD08p0002a0816" place="inline">今此四分律主
<lb ed="D" n="0002a09"/>即曇無&CB18786;部是此是梵語唐言法正部也。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a10"/><div2 type="note"><entry><form>得戒有十種</form><def><list><item id="itemD08p0002a1006">一自然得戒唯佛</item><item id="itemD08p0002a1013">二自誓得戒謂大迦
<lb ed="D" n="0002a11"/>葉</item><item id="itemD08p0002a1102">三見諦得戒謂五俱輪&CB21717;五比丘</item><item id="itemD08p0002a1115">四善來得戒謂耶
<lb ed="D" n="0002a12"/>&CB22064;&CB21717;</item><item id="itemD08p0002a1203">五三語得戒謂佛在世未制戒前但受三歸即得
<lb ed="D" n="0002a13"/>具&CB30133;</item><item id="itemD08p0002a1303">六問荅得戒謂&CB00824;&CB00442;耶沙&CB12752;年始七&CB15329;佛問
<pb ed="D" id="D08.8780.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/>其義一具荅稱可聖心便發具&CB30133;</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0114">七八敬得戒謂大
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/>愛道&CB30130;阿難聞八法<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">己</rdg></app>歡喜頂受便發具&CB30133;八敬者
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/>百罵舉授懺請安自</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0309">八遣使得戒謂半&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/>有其難緣差使&CB00855;戒即得具&CB30133;</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0413">九羯磨&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/>十僧&CB30848;法</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0505">十邊方五人授大戒</item></list><p id="pD08p0003a0513" place="inline">已前九種&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/>世羯磨一法教通&CB21868;聖被及僧&CB00112;說羅現未&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/>法。</p></def></entry></div2><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0003a0702" place="inline">問羯磨受戒具&CB30133;幾緣得名如法。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0003a0715" place="inline">荅依僧祇&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/>&CB10318;緣。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0003a0803">一年滿廿三衣&CB00425;具</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0811">二身&CB07099;遮難</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0816">三結界&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a09"/>四界內&CB16487;集</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0906">五羯磨成就</item><item id="itemD08p0003a0911">六十僧滿&CB30133;</item></list><p id="pD08p0003a0916" place="inline">&CB09113;此&unrec;…&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a10"/>如法闕一不成。</p></sp></dialog><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0003a1007" place="inline">問界有幾種。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0003a1012" place="inline">荅。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0003a1013">一者&CB30848;法界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1018"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">二者僧</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a11"/>界</item></list><p id="pD08p0003a1102" place="inline">&CB30848;法有三。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0003a1106">一者攝僧界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1111">二攝衣界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1115">三攝食界</item></list>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a12"/><p id="pD08p0003a1201">僧界有三種。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0003a1206">一者大界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1210">二者界&CB00588;</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1214">三者小界</item></list><p id="pD08p0003a1218" place="inline">今&unrec;&unrec;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a13"/>之內又有三種謂。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0003a1308">人法二同界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1313">法食二同界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1318">法同食
<lb ed="D" n="0003a14"/>別界</item></list><p id="pD08p0003a1403" place="inline">若就自然界中者則分四別。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0003a1414">一者謂聚落界</item>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a15"/><item id="itemD08p0003a1501">二者蘭若界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1506">三者道行界</item><item id="itemD08p0003a1511">四者木界</item></list></sp></dialog><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0003a1515" place="inline">問羯磨有
<pb ed="D" id="D08.8780.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a01"/>幾種。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0004a0103" place="inline">荅有一百卅四種。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0004a0110">單自羯磨有卅九</item><item id="itemD08p0004a0117">白二羯磨
<lb ed="D" n="0004a02"/>有五十七</item><item id="itemD08p0004a0205">自四羯磨卅八</item></list><p id="pD08p0004a0211" place="inline">此三羯磨攝一切羯皆&CB16487;。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a03"/><div2 type="note"><entry><form>明五篇法</form><def><list><item id="itemD08p0004a0305">一波羅夷篇<note place="inline">&CB02649;是西音此云&CB07099;餘若犯此戒永&CB00020;眾外故曰&CB07099;餘不得与僧同行布&CB16765;羯磨&CB00020;
<lb ed="D" n="0004a04"/>在界外故云餘&CB07099;</note></item><item id="itemD08p0004a0408">二僧伽婆尸沙篇<note place="inline">此云僧殘若犯此戒行則毀&CB21897;不應在布&CB16765;羯磨眾中之&CB21092;行類其人故名僧殘</note></item>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a05"/><item id="itemD08p0004a0501">三名波逸提篇<note place="inline">此云方&CB18944;若犯此戒&CB18944;落地獄燒&CB00827;覆障故云&CB18944;也</note></item><item id="itemD08p0004a0527">四名波羅提提&CB22064;&CB00112;篇<note place="inline">此云向彼悔
<lb ed="D" n="0004a06"/>若犯此戒事合可呵對手懺悔故云向彼悔</note></item><item id="itemD08p0004a0618">五名式叉迦羅&CB00112;篇<note place="inline">此方云應當學威儀練行懃習方成故云應當學</note></item></list></def></entry>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a07"/><entry><form>此明七聚法</form><def><list><item id="itemD08p0004a0706">一波羅夷聚</item><item id="itemD08p0004a0711">二僧伽婆尸沙聚</item><item id="itemD08p0004a0718">三偷蘭遮
<lb ed="D" n="0004a08"/>聚<note place="inline">此是梵語唐言&CB00308;&CB08891;亦云遮障偷言遮障蘭言鄣若犯此罪大遮障聖道故云遮障法偷蘭有四一五&CB01618;偷蘭應滅&CB04912;不可除二初篇下重
<lb ed="D" n="0004a09"/>偷蘭應八僧中悔三初篇下輕偷蘭二篇下重偷蘭應四僧中懺四獨頭蘭遮及餘篇下偷蘭應三僧中悔</note></item><item id="itemD08p0004a0942">四波逸提聚</item>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a10"/><item id="itemD08p0004a1001">五波羅提提&CB22064;&CB00112;聚</item><item id="itemD08p0004a1009">六突吉羅聚</item><item id="itemD08p0004a1014">七&CB08891;說聚<note place="inline">突吉羅者義翻
<lb ed="D" n="0004a11"/>云&CB08891;作突者名&CB08891;吉羅名作&CB08891;不止故名突吉羅所云蹉跦身作名&CB08891;口作名說故云&CB08891;&CB30848;&CB08891;&CB22072;突吉羅此二聚罪若故犯者應對手懺若&CB00386;犯應責懺</note></item></list></def></entry></div2>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0004a1201">問欲戒具幾緣成犯。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0004a1209" place="inline">荅具四緣。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0004a1213">一前境是女人</item><item id="itemD08p0004a1219">二興染心</item>
<pb ed="D" id="D08.8780.0005a" n="0005a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a01"/><item id="itemD08p0005a0101">三起方便</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0105">四与境合便犯</item></list></sp></dialog><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0005a0111" place="inline">問盜戒具幾緣成犯。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0005a0119" place="inline">荅具六緣成犯。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a02"/><list><item id="itemD08p0005a0201">有一主&CB21980;</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0205">二有主想</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0209">三有盜心</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0213">四重&CB21980;</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0216">五興方便</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0220">六離
<lb ed="D" n="0005a03"/>本&CB30529;便犯</item></list></sp></dialog><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0005a0305" place="inline">問煞戒具幾緣。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0005a0311" place="inline">荅具五緣。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0005a0315">一是人</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0318">二人想</item>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a04"/><item id="itemD08p0005a0401">三興&CB00517;</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0404">四起方便</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0408">五&CB07589;命根</item></list></sp></dialog><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0005a0412" place="inline">問大妄語戒具幾緣。</p></sp>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a05"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0005a0501">荅具八緣成犯。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0005a0507">一前境是人</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0512">二人想</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0515">三事&CB28933;</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0518">四知是&CB28933;
<lb ed="D" n="0005a06"/>事</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0602">五有誑他心</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0607">六自言已得</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0612">七言&CB08256;了了</item><item id="itemD08p0005a0617">八前人知解</item></list></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0005a0701">問僧有幾種。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0005a0706" place="inline">荅四種。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0005a0709">一者四人僧<note place="inline">除授戒自恣出罪銓一切羯磨應作</note></item>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a08"/><item id="itemD08p0005a0801">二者五人僧<note place="inline">除中國授戒出罪餘法得作</note></item><item id="itemD08p0005a0817">三者十人僧<note place="inline">除出罪餘法作</note></item><item id="itemD08p0005a0828">四者廿人僧<note place="inline">一切羯磨得作現復更多</note></item></list></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0005a0901">問菩&CB16765;戒中煞先&CB21942;後何故聲聞戒中&CB21942;先煞後。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pD08p0005a0920" place="inline">荅菩&CB16765;
<lb ed="D" n="0005a10"/>為大慈為本是以煞戒為初聲聞以梵行為機是以欲戒
<lb ed="D" n="0005a11"/>為首。</p></sp></dialog><div2 type="note"><entry place="inline"><form>受衣法</form><def><p id="pD08p0005a1106" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">若不持三衣入聚落者得無量罪世世
<lb ed="D" n="0005a12"/>裸形無有衣服若不串&CB00424;細入佫人家家得罪若食飲
<lb ed="D" n="0005a13"/>時&CB09727;得罪。</p></def></entry></div2><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pD08p0005a1305" place="inline">問云何名為三衣六&CB21980;。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><list><item id="itemD08p0005a1314"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">一名安陀會</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"></rdg></app><note place="inline">有四種一割截二攝業三褋&CB01007;四縵作一長一短割截衣持餘三累此改持</note></item>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a14"/><item id="itemD08p0005a1401">二名&CB00614;多羅僧<note place="inline">有二種一割截二褋&CB01007;二長一短即是七條衣受割截衣持若餘衣准此</note></item><item id="itemD08p0005a1435">三名僧伽梨<note place="inline">此衣有十
<lb ed="D" n="0005a15"/>八種謂割截褋&CB01007;各九品若受上衣廿五條四長一短割截衣持若是褋&CB01007;條&CB21092;准上褋&CB01007;衣持若中品三長一短若是下品二長一短</note></item></list></sp></dialog>
<pb ed="D" id="D08.8780.0006a" n="0006a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a01"/><div2 type="note"><entry><form>授衣文</form><def><p id="pD08p0006a0104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">大&CB18786;一心念&CB22329;比丘某甲此&CB00614;多羅僧七條衣受兩長
<lb ed="D" n="0006a02"/>一短割截衣持<note place="inline">三說若是餘衣及褋&CB01007;&CB00526;&CB01007;&CB21717;臨事准改受文同上</note>。</p></def></entry><entry place="inline"><form>&CB22057;衣文</form><def><p id="pD08p0006a0230" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">大&CB18786;一心念&CB22329;比
<lb ed="D" n="0006a03"/>丘某甲此僧伽梨是&CB22329;三衣&CB21092;先受持今&CB22057;<note place="inline">一說下二衣及&CB00112;五衣&CB21717;&CB00824;&CB22057;亦&CB07414;</note>。</p></def></entry>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a04"/><entry><form>授藥法</form><def><p id="pD08p0006a0404" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">藥有四種。</p><list><item id="itemD08p0006a0408">一時藥<note place="inline"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">佉</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>闍&CB00112;食有五種謂&CB00595;乾飯魚肉佉闍尼食梵音唐言枝&CB01007;花果細未食有五種一大淨二刀
<lb ed="D" n="0006a05"/>淨三瘡淨四鳥喙淨五不中種淨此中火淨及子壞淨得并子食餘三去子食是時藥謂&CB30130;旦至中前食若欲授者先知食體後知餘藥准此</note>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a06"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha"></lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">三非時藥<note place="inline">&CB16566;言蘇油生蘇蜜石蜜有病因緣應加授法</note></rdg></app></item>
